{"tid":2117429,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"英國牛津大學研發出疫苗初步顯示可助人體抗擊新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-07-21T00:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T00:41:52.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8f26f13b07d13b41373fbd0431f9ac89e07863","tid":2117429,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T00:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1538940_1_20200721021745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1538940_1_20200721021745.jpg&h=de894d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛津大學研發出一款疫苗，初步顯示有助訓練人體的免疫系統，對抗新型冠狀病毒。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n英國牛津大學與藥廠研發出一款疫苗，初步顯示有助訓練人體的免疫系統，對抗新型冠狀病毒，疫苗本身亦似乎可安全使用。<br />\n<br />\n研究團隊公布首階段測試數據，約一千人自願接受注射。研究發現，疫苗令他們產生可以抗擊病毒的抗體及白血球。白血球是免疫系統細胞，幫助身體抵抗細菌入侵及其他感染。<br />\n<br />\n報道說今次發現在抗疫方面帶來重大曙光，但這款疫苗能否提供充夠保護，仍然是言之尚早，有待進行更大規模的測試。雖然研究未有最終成果，但英國政府已經預訂一億劑這款疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538940-20200721.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538940-20200721.htm&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8QVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=9b8819df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538940-20200721.htm&h=2f638b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538940-20200721.htm</a>"},{"pid":"aac2151382d42495c4577d4071a777eb94090221","tid":2117429,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T00:35:27.000Z","msg":"希望係佢再變種之前出到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf6a9d6d69ffaf654dd6fe605104c24dd481c95","tid":2117429,"uid":302225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab8f26f13b07d13b41373fbd0431f9ac89e07863","tid":2117429,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T00:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/